ADMIN
   │
   ▼
BLOCKCHAIN (Deploys Contracts)
   │
   ▼
INSTITUTION → Generates DID → Registered On-Chain
   │
   ▼
INSTITUTION Issues VC → Signs VC
   │
   ▼
VC Uploaded to IPFS → CID Generated
   │
   ▼
CID + Metadata Stored On-Chain
   │
   ▼
Student Wallet Stores VC
   │
   ▼
Verifier Requests VC
   │
   ▼
Verifier Checks:
   • DID Registry
   • Hash Match
   • Revocation Status
   • Signature Validity
   ▼
Trust Decision
